10:21 ou) du/nasqe poth/rion kuri/ou pi/nein kai\ poth/rion daimoni/wn: ou) du/nasqe trape/zhj kuri/ou mete/xein kai\ trape/zhj daimoni/wn.
10:22 h)\ parazhlou=men to\n ku/rion; mh\ i)sxuro/teroi au)tou= e)smen;
