11:1 mimhtai/ mou gi/nesqe, kaqw\j ka)gw\ Xristou=.
11:2 )Epainw= de\ u(ma=j o(/ti pa/nta mou me/mnhsqe kai\ kaqw\j pare/dwka u(mi=n ta\j parado/seij kate/xete.
