11:6 ei) ga\r ou) katakalu/ptetai gunh/, kai\ keira/sqw: ei) de\ ai)sxro\n gunaiki\ to\ kei/rasqai h)\ cura=sqai, katakalupte/sqw.
11:7 a)nh\r me\n ga\r ou)k o)fei/lei katakalu/ptesqai th\n kefalh/n, ei)kw\n kai\ do/ca qeou= u(pa/rxwn: h( gunh\ de\ do/ca a)ndro/j e)stin.
