11:23 e)gw\ ga\r pare/labon a)po\ tou= kuri/ou, o(\ kai\ pare/dwka u(mi=n, o(/ti o( ku/rioj )Ihsou=j e)n th=| nukti\ h(=| paredi/deto e)/laben a)/rton
